query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'askubuntu',
'superuser',
'tex')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('active-directory',
'compression',
'fancyhdr',
'gcc',
'languages',
'logging',
'mp3',
'passwords',
'root',
'snow-leopard',
'texmaker',
'tikz-arrows',
'windows-subsystem-for-linux',
'youtube',
'zip')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000 group by t1.name;
